history.content:
CS170 + Stat C100 + CS 186 is definitely doable, CS 170 + Stat C100 + another course is ok as well

=======================

CS170 + Stat C100 + CS 186/184 should be ok. 

189 depends on if you have excellent backgrounds on math53/54/ee16a/ee16b and can have a lot of workload in Fall. It's common for people who has not taken all of 53+ee16ab or 5354ee16b to spend a ton of time self-studying missed materials for 189 and I remember in last Fall there dropped ~300+ people from 189. 

CS170 + Stat C100 + 162 is tough but doable
